name: Rincon Exchange
overview:
Rincon Exchange is located in Santa Barbara, California, known as the arm of Rincon Technology in e-commerce and the leading supplier of network gears. Their products includes switches, routers, servers and storage, optical networking, and other accessories.

In need of network equipment but have less budget for it? Rincon Exchange can be the quit you are looking for. The company and selling used network equipment and gears. Every product undergo detail testing before made available for sale.

Every item is proven working and reliable. Their manufacturers includes Cisco, Junifer, Ciena, Bellair, Suns, Nortel, Alcatel-Lucent, Erisson, Arris and other known brands in computer networking.
